    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> to a bowl</p><p>Once the pepper is tender, remove the tray[s] from the oven</p><p>Transfer the <strong>tender</strong> <strong>pepper </strong>to the bowl and set aside to marinate</p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for 10-15 min further, or until the chips are golden and crisp</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1658226067252-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1658226067252-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
