            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1658226078952-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1658226078952-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To assemble your sandwich, spread a little<strong> herby aioli </strong>over each <strong>ciabatta base</strong> and top with the <strong>marinated pepper</strong> and the <strong>crispy hake</strong>, then finish with the <strong>ciabatta lid</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> salad</strong>, <strong>chips</strong> and <strong>remaining herby aioli</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle the salad with some of the <strong>reserved balsamic vinegar</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
